    <section_number>30</section_number>
    <catch_line>Arbitrator; Requirements</catch_line>
    <order_by>30</order_by>
    <text>
        The single arbitrator, whether agreed upon by the parties or selected by the board of conciliation and arbitration, shall be a legal resident of the commonwealth and shall be experienced in state and local finance.
    </text>
